/* MATGRADIENT.SRC -- This ia a library of gradient procedures for various matrix set-ups */
/* All gradients are such that they are taken with respect to the elements of the upper triangle of symmetric matrices
   Tested and validated all these procedures; see gradient test.gau in d:\gauss\com\nonnormal
   
   ON OCT 23, 2025, MOVED         dg = zeros(parmCor,parmCor); TO LINE 886 FROM EARLIER LINE 883 

